OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly dry
OL,6,Fevening with some sunny spells, but
OL,7,Fwith a few scattered showers around.
OL,8,FOvernight more in the way of clear
OL,9,Fperiods, and becoming chilly.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA cold, but sunny start to
OL,12,Fthe day. Cloud then building to bring
OL,13,Fa few showers from mid morning but
OL,14,Fmany places staying dry, with further
OL,15,Fsunny spells later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
